data.description: Large Lot, Large Rooms, Huge backyard space and more - they just don't make them quite like they used to! Located in well established Meadow Park Estates, this home is zoned for exemplary rated Butler Elementary.  Rich wood ceiling beams, vaulted ceilings, wood paneling, brick wood burning fireplace, built ins and more add to the interior appeal of this gem. Primary bedroom has en suite bath with dual vanities, stand alone shower, deep soaking tub, and large walk in closet. Second full bath is designated to the secondary bedrooms and sets in between the two. ALL rooms are graciously sized and the full renovations in both bathrooms lend even more to the most aesthetically appealing surround. Take your breath away in the expansive private fenced in backyard. Driveway is swing drive and has privacy gate that closes in the yard and garage. Home is close to fine dining, entertainment, shopping and more. Less that a half mile walk to Gibbins Park and 5 minute drive to Legacy Nature Park.
